parameters:
I have my own room too... but I might prefer... spending
time here with everyone...

...As for Vega, you know... she drinks a lot of water while
studying, so she goes to the bathroom... quite frequently...

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The
flames here are the most comforting.
\SE[33]Ugh... My stomach feels like it's about to burst...

\SE[58]You shouldn't force yourself to eat so much...
Laura's stomach looks like that of a pregnant woman.
\SE[3]She's turned into a maternity dress.

\SE[51]I ended up eating so much because Vita was eating a
lot... \!\SE[92]And if I waste food, Luna will get mad at
me...

\SE[4]But if you eat that much, you'll get fat, you know?
\SE[3]It's fine for me because no matter how much I eat, I
don't gain weight... But if I get influenced, I'll end up
getting all chubby.

\SE[102]What's that, it's not fair...! \SE[114]...I mean,
what should I do with this kind of stomach!? I might really
end up being hated...!?

\SE[39]No... It's okay. \SE[2]Lunaroa will love you no
matter what kind of Laura you are. Her love won't waver just
because of that.

\SE[56]And if Lunaroa couldn't forgive the overeating...
\SE[3]I'm sure she would forcefully stick her fingers into
Laura's mouth and make her vomit everything she ate.

\SE[14]No way... Can you really say that? \SE[15]It's a
quick way to prevent Laura from getting fat... Lunaroa is
the type of girl who likes to be mean to the person she
likes.

\SE[38]With a twisted expression of anguish, Luna sticks her
fingers into Laura's mouth as she continues to vomit, all
while smiling. \SE[15]Can you really say that it's truly
impossible...?

\SE[102]Ugh... I can't say for sure... I... I still...
\SE[51]Even someone like me... I... I can't go that far...
\SE[4]Welcome back~. Oh, Vega is with you too?

\SE[2]Hey, you two just arrived in this country, right?
\.As a guide, I brought the two of you along. \!\SE[2]So...
if it's okay with you, \.I was wondering...

\SE[2]If I were to take in a lodging, it would cost money
too... \SE[5]I want to let Vega live in this house... Is
that not possible?

\SE[22]Sure, of course! \SE[21]It seems like it'll be fun,
like a girls' dormitory.

\SE[74]...Honestly, that would be helpful. \SE[7]Well then,
I'll be a bother for a while.

\SE[16]Eh?! I am a free-spirited stray cat after all!
\SE[0]I can live more comfortably scavenging for leftovers
in the cold, lonely streets than in a warm home!

\SE[2]Besides, once you experience the peace of having a
home, your human strength will decrease! \SE[11]To live
strongly, this is enough!

\SE[10]That... Maybe it would be better to reevaluate your
life...

\SE[16]Thank you for your consideration! \!\SE[25]Well then,
the cold sky is calling me, so I'll be around here! \.Please
take care of my sister! \.\SE[16]That's all!!

\SE[74]Why are you acting like a guardian in a slightly
awkward way...

\SE[2]Then, about Vega's room... \SE[2]Oh, maybe it's
better to eat first? \SE[2]You two have already eaten,
right?

\SE[2]Oh, right... Laura ate too much. \SE[1]We were
discussing whether it would be better for Lunaroa to make
her throw up.

\SE[116]Wait, no!! \SE[33]What are we going to do if Lunaroa
really awakens to that...!

\SE[72]Honestly... It seems like it's going to be a noisy
life...
